{"tid":1438860,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"多謝政府spin 番入正題 民間記者會可以recall 市民記憶","createTime":"2019-08-10T02:13:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T12:22:25.000Z","uid":171788,"like":66,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"238617b47b3ef5d7c8919f866a47c43f54aa437d","tid":1438860,"uid":171788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T02:13:52.000Z","msg":"林鄭講民生 講經濟 <br />\n<br />\n下一次民間記者會 <br />\n可以拎番哂之前 送中條例 外資反應<br />\n過唔到 議員回應 （民建聯轉駄） <br />\n再拎警民衝突嘅相<br />\n官黑勾結 (何妖握手相）<br />\n一切一切都係港共政府 &ldquo;共孽&rdquo; 令香港經濟受到衝撃<br />\n市民唔可以安居樂業 <br />\n<br />\n之後最尾spin 到 送中條例 仍然起立法會議程入面<br />\n用 黃宏發 無暫援 條片作結<br />\n<br />\n然後問番香港人而家一樣都未爭取到 未平息民忿嘅林鄭政府 係咪仲有面講叫人攪經濟 攪民生 ！ 市民唔係你嘅奴隸 唔係你犯左錯 你可以唔回應！ <br />\n<br />\n運動再入番正題 ！"},{"pid":"7c3db3a3c6b68c89c083131c9ea6750a805a9e78","tid":1438860,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T02:16:13.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"20a595910a3816f26b8f3e57a7ad1e8fbbbdba2f","tid":1438860,"uid":170974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T02:21:08.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1f28fca03f642ae3302cf87cde347dbb943f32e2","tid":1438860,"uid":171788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T02:21:30.000Z","msg":"Push !"},{"pid":"2de15873915c509ed7eeeccade2c8605abc544e2","tid":1438860,"uid":171788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T02:26:35.000Z","msg":"仲可以問 張曉明 係咪authorize 林鄭 有咁嘅權無視香港市民 ！ 如果係 係咪與民為敵"},{"pid":"7aa9ce62c8368cdc1ee7bd40a926551bec924674","tid":1438860,"uid":171788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T02:30:31.000Z","msg":"Push !"},{"pid":"f01f3fd436a7627d52f7ba03a848e632d42e8455","tid":1438860,"uid":171788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T02:34:52.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"75546ac8f240af6c1a60dc1b9c1a41fb7bf65f3c","tid":1438860,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T02:39:56.000Z","msg":"岩"}